{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"528","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"上市公司法說 9月連發","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:'>2019-08-29 00:35</span><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;12.0pt;font-family:'>經濟日報 記者盧宏奇／台北報導</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>臺灣證券交易所公布，<span lang='EN-US'>9</span>月預計有新海（<span lang='EN-US'>9926</span>）等<span lang='EN-US'>21</span>家上市公司將假證交所場地自行辦理法人說明會。至<span lang='EN-US'>7</span>月底止，國內上市公司總計已辦理<span lang='EN-US'>907</span>家次法說會。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;<img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E6%B3%95%E8%AA%AA1.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 450px;' /></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'>臺灣證券交易所公布，<span lang='EN-US'>9</span>月預計有新海（<span lang='EN-US'>9926</span>）等<span lang='EN-US'>21</span>家上市公司將假證交所場地自行辦理法人說明會。至<span lang='EN-US'>7</span>月底止，國內上市公司總計已辦理<span lang='EN-US'>907</span>家次法說會。 （聯合報系資料庫）</span></p>\n\n<hr />\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>證交所資料顯示，<span lang='EN-US'>9</span>月<span lang='EN-US'>2</span>日新海、大洋，<span lang='EN-US'>9</span>月<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>日福壽、全國電，<span lang='EN-US'>9</span>月<span lang='EN-US'>6</span>日台聚、中石化，<span lang='EN-US'>9</span>月<span lang='EN-US'>9</span>日揚博，<span lang='EN-US'>9</span>月<span lang='EN-US'>10</span>日新紡，共計有<span lang='EN-US'>8</span>家上市公司將於<span lang='EN-US'>9</span>月上旬赴證交所舉行法說。</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>接下來為<span lang='EN-US'>9</span>月<span lang='EN-US'>11</span>日富爾特，<span lang='EN-US'>9</span>月<span lang='EN-US'>12</span>日元禎，<span lang='EN-US'>9</span>月<span lang='EN-US'>17</span>日無敵，<span lang='EN-US'>9</span>月<span lang='EN-US'>19</span>日大華金、陞泰，<span lang='EN-US'>9</span>月<span lang='EN-US'>20</span>日競國、智邦，<span lang='EN-US'>9</span>月中旬預計有<span lang='EN-US'>7</span>家上市公司辦理法說會。</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>至於<span lang='EN-US'>9</span>月下旬排定的六家上市公司，有<span lang='EN-US'>9</span>月<span lang='EN-US'>23</span>日的偉全、永信，<span lang='EN-US'>9</span>月<span lang='EN-US'>24</span>日的台榮，<span lang='EN-US'>9</span>月<span lang='EN-US'>26</span>日的晶相光，<span lang='EN-US'>9</span>月<span lang='EN-US'>27</span>日的欣天然、中工。</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>依據最近股價表現來看，包括台聚、智邦、晶相光等三檔都有不錯表現，屆時可望成為較熱門的法說場次。</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>為提升上市公司財務、業務資訊透明度，並增進投資人獲取企業訊息的管道，證交所已規範本國上市公司應定期在中華民國境內自辦或受邀參加法說會。</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>證交所表示，法說會是上市公司對外溝通管道之一，除適時向投資大眾說明營運績效及對未來產業前景的看法、傳達經營理念與企業價值，使股東或潛在投資人進一步瞭解企業營運發展機會或挑戰外，並提供投資人表達意見或與公司雙向交流的機會，進而提升公司治理品質。</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>證交所亦歡迎上市公司與證交所聯繫，免費借用證交所場地辦理法說會，以提升公司資訊透明度。</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='text-align: center;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;<img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E6%B3%95%E8%AA%AA2.jpg' style='width: 550px; height: 422px;' /></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: center;'><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:'>9</span><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:'>月將赴證交所舉行法說上市公司 圖／經濟日報提供</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'>資料來源：<span lang='EN-US'>https://udn.com/news/story/7251/4015742</span></span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2019-09-04","clk_count":"231"}},"__N_SSG":true}